data.description: Motivated sellers! Beautiful, barely lived in home built by Centex homes in December 2021. Seller offering $3000 to go towards rate buy down or closing!  home to 366 Bedford Falls Lane, in charming Sonterra, a master-planned community. The home welcomes you with large foyer and an office with french doors. This office could easily be converted into one of the secondary bedrooms. The home then opens into the large living room and kitchen, with beautiful views of the backyard. No neighbors are behind the house, just a greenbelt. The gourmet kitchen has an eat-in bar and room for a dining table and extra large walk-in pantry. Stainless appliances and granite countertops make this kitchen modern and elegant. The primary bedroom is up the stairs and has a large double vanity and large walk-in closet. There is also a large gameroom as another living area as well as two other secondary bedrooms. The laundry room is upstairs as well. This is a home you don't want to miss out on! The lot is over-sized and has been well-taken care of! If you have a first time home buyer, they may be able to qualify for the assumable mortgage. Ask me how!
